    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your ticket has arrived - and it's inviting you to the Mind Garden!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/cea36708969cc60db69f89bde1de74f5.webp?t=1752867332\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/cea36708969cc60db69f89bde1de74f5.poster.avif?t=1752867332\" class=\"bb_img\" width=300 height=145 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the weight of memory becomes too much, retreat into the Mind Garden—a place where time flows differently and healing awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awaken at dawn in a surreal garden populated with residents who seem to know more about you than they initially reveal. Complete simple quests throughout a single day, collect memories for a mysterious flame growing at the heart of a tree, and slowly piece together fragments of yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the day progresses, so does your journey toward an uncomfortable truth. The garden holds answers, but are you ready to face what you've been avoiding?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/579d0d09d898891845519b2052aaac08.poster.avif?t=1752867332\" width=74 height=76 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/579d0d09d898891845519b2052aaac08.webm?t=1752867332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mind Garden</strong> is a short, intimate experience (1-2 hours) featuring handcrafted artwork scanned from original crayon drawings and real childhood videos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep a journal of your discoveries, interact with the garden's quirky inhabitants, and decide whether to remain in blissful detachment or confront what lies beyond the garden's boundaries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the space between memory and reality, sometimes the only path forward requires courage—and fire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>A personal, poetic journey about finding the strength to face what we've locked away.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/7708ac0d5cf40180d1a12545f05bdb18.poster.avif?t=1752867332\" width=500 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/7708ac0d5cf40180d1a12545f05bdb18.webm?t=1752867332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045100/extras/7708ac0d5cf40180d1a12545f05bdb18.mp4?t=1752867332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
